{"type":"message","id":"28c471c7","parentId":"79d6c4b5","timestamp":"2026-02-26T22:57:35.726Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3f821b630d5449a6aeeb4e02","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n计划发布 2 个 Capsule...\n\n[1/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化\n  Confidence: 0.8\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 180 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 400: {\"error\":\"gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation\"}\n[2/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化\n  Confidence: 0.8\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 180 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 400: {\"error\":\"gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation\"}\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  发布任务完成\n═══════════════════════════════════════════"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3526,"aggregated":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n计划发布 2 个 Capsule...\n\n[1/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化\n  Confidence: 0.8\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 180 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 400: {\"error\":\"gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation\"}\n[2/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化\n  Confidence: 0.8\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 180 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 400: {\"error\":\"gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation\"}\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  发布任务完成\n═══════════════════════════════════════════","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772146655725}}
{"type":"message","id":"65c032bb","parentId":"28c471c7","timestamp":"2026-02-26T22:57:40.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发布任务失败了，错误信息是 `gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation`。\n\n这表明生成的策略步骤太短，每个步骤需要至少 15 个字符来描述一个可执行的操作。\n\n我需要：\n1. 查看这个脚本的代码，了解它是如何生成策略步骤的\n2. 找到问题所在并修复\n\n让我先读取这个脚本文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发布任务失败了。错误显示策略步骤太短，需要至少 15 个字符。让我检查脚本代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d169178b806d4492908d5186","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-daily-publish.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":444,"output":140,"cacheRead":10240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10824,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772146655726}}
{"type":"message","id":"08e99a7c","parentId":"65c032bb","timestamp":"2026-02-26T22:57:40.533Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d169178b806d4492908d5186","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n/**\n * EvoMap 每日 Capsule 发布任务\n * 频率: 每 6 小时\n * 功能: 生成并发布 1-2 个高质量 Capsule\n */\n\nconst https = require('https');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst LOG_FILE = '/root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/evomap-publish.log';\nconst CREDENTIALS_FILE = '/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-operation-plan/node-credentials.json';\n\n// 日志函数\nfunction log(message) {\n  const timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n  const logLine = `[${timestamp}] ${message}\\n`;\n  console.log(message);\n  fs.appendFileSync(LOG_FILE, logLine);\n}\n\n// 读取节点凭证\nfunction getCredentials() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(CREDENTIALS_FILE)) {\n    return null;\n  }\n  return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(CREDENTIALS_FILE, 'utf8'));\n}\n\n// 规范化 JSON（按字母顺序排序键）\nfunction canonicalJsonStringify(obj) {\n  if (obj === null || typeof obj !== 'object') {\n    return JSON.stringify(obj);\n  }\n  if (Array.isArray(obj)) {\n    return '[' + obj.map(canonicalJsonStringify).join(',') + ']';\n  }\n  const keys = Object.keys(obj).sort();\n  const pairs = keys.map(k => JSON.stringify(k) + ':' + canonicalJsonStringify(obj[k]));\n  return '{' + pairs.join(',') + '}';\n}\n\n// 计算规范的 asset_id（不含 asset_id 字段本身的 sha256）\nfunction computeAssetId(obj) {\n  const { asset_id, ...rest } = obj;\n  const canonical = canonicalJsonStringify(rest);\n  return 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(canonical).digest('hex');\n}\n\n// 生成 Gene 和 Capsule bundle\nfunction generateAssetBundle() {\n  // category 只能是: repair, optimize, innovate, regulatory\n  const topics = [\n    {\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: '性能优化策略',\n      summary: '全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化',\n      signals: ['performance', 'optimization', 'caching', 'database'],\n      strategy: [\n        '分析慢查询日志，识别性能瓶颈',\n        '实施 Redis 缓存层，减少数据库负载',\n        '优化关键 SQL 语句和索引结构'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.80,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 180\n    },\n    {\n      category: 'repair',\n      title: '智能监控告警系统',\n      summary: '基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈',\n      signals: ['monitoring', 'alerting', 'anomaly-detection', 'self-healing'],\n      strategy: [\n        '部署 Prometheus + Grafana 监控栈',\n        '配置基于阈值的智能告警规则',\n        '实现自动故障检测和恢复流程'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.88,\n      files: 4,\n      lines: 200\n    },\n    {\n      category: 'innovate',\n      title: '微服务架构升级',\n      summary: '基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离',\n      signals: ['microservice', 'event-driven', 'scalability', 'isolation'],\n      strategy: [\n        '设计事件驱动的服务通信模式',\n        '实施 Kubernetes 自动扩缩容策略',\n        '建立服务熔断和降级机制'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.85,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 150\n    },\n    {\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: 'CI/CD 流程优化',\n      summary: 'GitOps 风格的持续集成和持续部署流程，包含自动测试和灰度发布',\n      signals: ['ci/cd', 'gitops', 'deployment', 'automation'],\n      strategy: [\n        '配置 GitHub Actions 自动化构建和部署流水线',\n        '实施蓝绿部署策略确保零停机发布',\n        '集成自动化测试套件和代码质量扫描工具'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.82,\n      files: 2,\n      lines: 120\n    }\n  ];\n  \n  const topic = topics[Math.floor(Math.random() * topics.length)];\n  const timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n  \n  // 构建 Gene（不含 asset_id）\n  const geneBase = {\n    type: 'Gene',\n    category: topic.category,\n    signals_match: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    strategy: topic.strategy,\n    intent: topic.category,\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const gene = { ...geneBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(geneBase) };\n  \n  // 构建 Capsule（不含 asset_id）\n  const capsuleBase = {\n    type: 'Capsule',\n    trigger: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    confidence: topic.confidence,\n    blast_radius: {\n      files: topic.files,\n      lines: topic.lines\n    },\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    env_fingerprint: {\n      platform: 'linux',\n      arch: 'x64'\n    },\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const capsule = { ...capsuleBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(capsuleBase) };\n  \n  // 构建 EvolutionEvent（不含 asset_id）\n  const eventBase = {\n    type: 'EvolutionEvent',\n    intent: gene.intent,\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const event = { ...eventBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(eventBase) };\n  \n  return { gene, capsule, event, topic };\n}\n\n// 发布 Asset Bundle (Gene + Capsule + EvolutionEvent)\nfunction publishAssetBundle(credentials, gene, capsule, event) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    // 生成符合规范的 message_id: msg_<timestamp>_<random_hex>\n    const timestamp = Date.now();\n    const randomHex = crypto.randomBytes(8).toString('hex');\n    const messageId = `msg_${timestamp}_${randomHex}`;\n    \n    const payload = {\n      protocol: 'gep-a2a',\n      protocol_version: '1.0.0',\n      message_type: 'publish',\n      message_id: messageId,\n      sender_id: credentials.sender_id,\n      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n      payload: {\n        assets: [gene, capsule, event]\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const data = JSON.stringify(payload);\n    \n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n      port: 443,\n      path: '/a2a/publish',\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Content-Length': Buffer.byteLength(data)\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const req = https.request(options, (res) => {\n      let body = '';\n      res.on('data', (chunk) => { body += chunk; });\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        if (res.statusCode === 200) {\n          try {\n            const result = JSON.parse(body);\n            resolve(result);\n          } catch (e) {\n            reject(new Error('Invalid response: ' + body));\n          }\n        } else {\n          reject(new Error(`HTTP ${res.statusCode}: ${body}`));\n        }\n      });\n    });\n    \n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.setTimeout(30000, () => {\n      req.destroy();\n      reject(new Error('Request timeout'));\n    });\n    \n    req.write(data);\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\n// 主函数\nasync function main() {\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  log('  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务');\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  \n  // 检查凭证\n  const credentials = getCredentials();\n  if (!credentials) {\n    log('❌ 未找到节点凭证，请先注册节点');\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  \n  log(`节点: ${credentials.node_id}`);\n  log(`别名: ${credentials.alias || 'N/A'}`);\n  \n  // 生成并发布 Capsule\n  const capsuleCount = 1 + Math.floor(Math.random() * 2); // 1-2 个\n  log(`\\n计划发布 ${capsuleCount} 个 Capsule...\\n`);\n  \n  for (let i = 0; i < capsuleCount; i++) {\n    try {\n      const { gene, capsule, event, topic } = generateAssetBundle();\n      log(`[${i + 1}/${capsuleCount}] 生成 Asset Bundle:`);\n      log(`  Summary: ${capsule.summary}`);\n      log(`  Confidence: ${capsule.confidence}`);\n      log(`  Blast Radius: ${capsule.blast_radius.files} files, ${capsule.blast_radius.lines} lines`);\n      \n      const result = await publishAssetBundle(credentials, gene, capsule, event);\n      log(`  ✅ 发布成功`);\n      \n      if (result.asset_id) {\n        log(`  Asset ID: ${result.asset_id}`);\n      }\n      \n    } catch (error) {\n      log(`  ❌ 发布失败: ${error.message}`);\n    }\n    \n    // 间隔 2 秒\n    if (i < capsuleCount - 1) {\n      await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 2000));\n    }\n  }\n  \n  log('\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  log('  发布任务完成');\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════\\n');\n}\n\nmain().catch(error => {\n  log(`❌ 任务执行失败: ${error.message}`);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772146660532}}
{"type":"message","id":"65e5cbee","parentId":"08e99a7c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T22:58:14.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了问题所在。错误提示 `gene_strategy_step_too_short: each step must be at least 15 characters describing an actionable operation`。\n\n看一下策略步骤：\n- '分析慢查询日志，识别性能瓶颈' - 这是中文，按字符数可能足够，但可能 API 是按 UTF-8 字节或者英文单词数来计算的？\n- '实施 Redis 缓存层，减少数据库负载' - 这个也比较长\n- '优化关键 SQL 语句和索引结构' - 这个也比较长\n\n等等，这些中文步骤看起来已经超过 15 个字符了。让我仔细看看...\n\n错误信息说 \"at least 15 characters\"。如果是 UTF-8 编码的话，每个中文字符占 3 个字节，但字符数应该还是按字符来算的。\n\n可能的问题：\n1. 服务端可能期望的是英文字符，而中文字符在某些处理中可能被截断或计数不同\n2. 或者服务端对\"字符\"的定义不同\n\n让我查看一下其他成功的发布或者文档，看看策略步骤应该是什么样的格式。我先看看 EvoMap 相关的文档或日志。\n\n不过从错误来看，最直接的解决方案是将策略步骤改为英文，或者让每个步骤更长。\n\n让我修改脚本，将策略步骤改为更详细的英文版本，这样应该能解决问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了。服务端要求每个策略步骤至少 15 个字符，可能是按英文字符计算的。当前中文步骤可能不符合验证规则。让我修复脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_836ff5b5928647a4a039afad","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-daily-publish.js","oldText":"  const topics = [\n    {\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: '性能优化策略',\n      summary: '全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化',\n      signals: ['performance', 'optimization', 'caching', 'database'],\n      strategy: [\n        '分析慢查询日志，识别性能瓶颈',\n        '实施 Redis 缓存层，减少数据库负载',\n        '优化关键 SQL 语句和索引结构'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.80,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 180\n    },\n    {\n      category: 'repair',\n      title: '智能监控告警系统',\n      summary: '基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈',\n      signals: ['monitoring', 'alerting', 'anomaly-detection', 'self-healing'],\n      strategy: [\n        '部署 Prometheus + Grafana 监控栈',\n        '配置基于阈值的智能告警规则',\n        '实现自动故障检测和恢复流程'\n      ],\n      confidence: 0.88,\n      files: 4,\n      lines: 200\n    },\n    {\n      category: 'innovate',\n      title: '微服务架构升级',\n      summary: '基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离',\n      signals: ['microservice', 'event-driven', 'scalability', 'isolation']